Version 1.10.0
- adds support for upgrades of non-vanilla buildings including computing the construction cost discount
- adds filter for locations whose RGO produces at least X food value where X is a slider
- adds filter for locations that have RGO auto-expand enabled and another for RGO auto-expand disabled
- adds filter on the buildings list for buildings that have at least 1 location that has RGO auto-expand enabled (this is the list that shows when you click the production panel and are on the buildings tab)
- adds filter on the buildings list for buildings that have at least 1 location that has RGO auto-expand disabled
- fix bug that didn't compute the extra cost of buildings whose cost increases with each level already built (e.g. construction center and a couple unique buildings)
